Class Pcc

java.lang.Object
algo.Pcc
public class Pcc
extends java.lang.Object
This class computes and stores the shortest ways between pickUp and delivery points.

  • Method Details

    • computePcc

      public CompleteGraph computePcc()
      Computes lowest costs between pickup and delivery points. Stores the predecessors to be able to travel from a point to another. Returns a Complete graph to compute an optimized tour.
      Returns:
      Object CompleteGraph with costs to go from an intersection to another

    • computeWaysList

      public java.util.List<Way> computeWaysList​(java.util.List<Intersection> interList)
      Return a list of ways from a list of intersections. The list of intersections come from a order of visit computed by the TSP algo or from a user modification.
      Parameters:
      interList - List of intersections which represents classified
      Returns:
      A list of ways which contains all the segments to run the tour and some informations about time spent on each point.

    • changeOrder

      public Tour changeOrder​(Tour tour, Intersection intersection, int shift)
      Enable to modify the position of an intersection It's not possible to change the position of the start point.
      Parameters:
      tour - Contains the current order between pick up and delivery points.
      intersection - The intersection to change
      shift - Integer which represents the shift in the order. Can be positive or negative.
      Returns:
      A new Tour updated

    • addRequest

      public Tour addRequest​(Tour tour, Intersection pickup, Intersection delivery, java.lang.Integer pickUpDuration, java.lang.Integer deliveryDuration, java.lang.Integer pickupIndex, java.lang.Integer deliveryIndex)
      Enable to add a request. Add a pickup and a delivery point at a specific index.
      Parameters:
      tour - Contains the current order between pick up and delivery points.
      pickup - The pickup intersection to add
      delivery - The delivery intersection to add
      pickUpDuration - Time spent in seconds at pick up point
      deliveryDuration - Time spent in seconds at delivery point
      pickupIndex - Index where the pick up point will be added
      deliveryIndex - Index where the delivery point will be added
      Returns:
      A new Tour updated
